near resonance with a pair of levels $a$ and $b$, i.e.,
$\omega \approx \Omega_{ab}$, Eq. (14), as shown in Appendix A, becomes
$$
\begin{aligned}
\dot{\sigma}_{lm} &= -i[\Omega_{lm} - \sum_j(\Gamma_{lj}-\Gamma_{jm})\sigma_{jj}(t)]\sigma_{lm} \\\\
